### Aedes Mosquitos

$\cfrac{dP}{dt} = {b_{1}}(N_{M}-q_{1}I_{M})- \theta{P}$

$\cfrac{dQ}{dt} = {b_{1}}q_{1}I_{M}- \theta{Q}$

$\cfrac{dS_{M}}{dt} = \theta{P} - \frac{\beta_{ML}S_{M}I_{L}}{N_{L}} - \mu_{M}S_{M}$

$\cfrac{dE_{M}}{dt} = \frac{\beta_{ML}S_{M}I_{L}}{N_{L}} - \alpha_{M}E_{M} -\mu_{M}E_{M}$

$\cfrac{dI_{M}}{dt} = \theta{Q} + \alpha_{M}E_{M} -\mu_{M}I_{M}$


###Livestock


$\cfrac{dS_{L}}{dt} = N_{L}\mu_{L} - \frac{\beta_{LM}S_{L}I_{M}}{N_{M}}- \mu_{L}S_{L}$

$\cfrac{dE_{L}}{dt} =  \frac{\beta_{LM}S_{L}I_{M}}{N_{M}}- \alpha_{L}E_{L} - \mu_{L}E_{L}$

$\cfrac{dI_{L}}{dt} = \alpha_{L}E_{L} - \gamma{I_{L}} -  \mu_{L}I_{L} - d_{L}I_{L}$

$\cfrac{dInci_{L}}{dt} = \alpha_{L}E_{L}$
